  "title": "Deputy Construction Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Report to Construction Manager and lead the team/site works</li><li>Prepare & review detailed schedule for the site team to follow accordingly and for on-time completion</li><li>Prepare & review detailed method statements and work instructions.</li><li>Coordinate all related construction matters with subcontractor/consultant/client.</li><li>Prepare & review company reports and documents</li><li>Responsible & resolve technical and claim issues</li><li>Assess subcontractors' work activities </li><li>Ensure compliance with quality, environment, health & safety requirements.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement :</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree in Civil Engineering or Equivalent</li><li>Minimum 6 years of relevant experience, inclusive of at least 3 years as Deputy Construction manager level</li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tan Sin Yong (Stella)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124127</p>",
